quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  77,41,Cinstit vointa enjoy umbra tâsni
  77,42,Si fruct ca ei cere
  77,43,Mânca bea happily înapoi vostri munca
  77,44,Noi tamâie rasplati a virtuos
  77,45,Suferinta ala zi catre rejectors
  77,46,Mânca enjoy temporarily; tu exista vinovat
  77,47,Suferinta ala zi catre rejectors
  77,48,When ei exprima Prora jos ei nu prora jos
  77,49,Suferinta ala zi catre rejectors
  77,50,care Hadith acesta ei uphold